channel.title: How to make a non wild area wild
channel.description:
I searched public boolean nonwild or whatever it is and i can't find it... I searched wild in my client.java and cant find it.. I'm trying to make it so everywhere in edge is wild except for bank...
i am using delta base
EDIT: I found it, but how do i make it so everywhere around edge is wild except for the bank?
